{"word":"journey","count":1},{"word":"firm","count":1},{"word":"belief","count":1},{"word":"hearts","count":1},{"word":"guide","count":1},{"word":"darkness","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"wondering","count":1},{"word":"bring","count":1},{"word":"proceed","count":1},{"word":"b-but","count":1},{"word":"filled","count":1},{"word":"mom's","count":1},{"word":"love","count":1},{"word":"plant","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"busy","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"watered","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"hoping","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"short","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"sweetie","count":1},{"word":"natural","count":1},{"word":"cycle","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"understood","count":1},{"word":"reminds","count":1},{"word":"miss","count":1},{"word":"probably","count":1},{"word":"using","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"holding","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"play","count":1},{"word":"game","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"grown-ups","count":1},{"word":"exist","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"grown","count":1},{"word":"must've","count":1},{"word":"surprise","count":1},{"word":"managed","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"nice","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"okay","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"th-thank","count":1},{"word":"ready","count":1},{"word":"umm","count":1},{"word":"stage","count":1},{"word":"wooly","count":1},{"word":"trying","count":1},{"word":"three","count":1},{"word":"relics","count":1},{"word":"w-will","count":1},{"word":"moral","count":1},{"word":"feelings","count":1},{"word":"iris","count":1},{"word":"full","count":1},{"word":"blooming","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"exists","count":1},{"word":"believe","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"incredible","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"They look really angry...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"R-really?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"So... Is this the sword in the story that can slice through anything?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Hmm... The sword's actually made out of wood, and it's missing a small piece too.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Yeah, it looks like it's made out of wood. I don't think it's gonna cut anything really...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Look, there's a letter.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Hmm...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"My dear little warrior, you've found the first relic!\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Right now you must be thinking, 'What a plain-looking sword.'\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"How could this ordinary wooden sword possibly be the legendary Sword of Courage?\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Don't feel disappointed just yet, think back on what you've been through so far.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"All the challenges you've faced along the way. The waves under your feet felt so high to you, and the treasure chest above seemed ever so far away.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Yet still you continued to climb the mountains, every step of the way, until you finally reached the peak. Your courage has been heard.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"And this seemingly ordinary wooden sword...\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Yeah, that's what it says in the letter. How did you know, Encore?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Ah. Y-yes!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"It goes on to say, \"Oh, little warrior, your adventure doesn't end here.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"To have your wishes come true, courage alone is not enough.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"You need not look far, as the shield that symbolizes faith is buried right beneath your very feet.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"In a land covered in sand, treasures may lay, or there may be nothing at all.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"A land covered in sand...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"O-Okay.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"It's also made of wood...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"O-Okay. Let's see here. It says...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Congratulations again to you, my little warrior.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Although the bulk of your efforts were in vain, you did not give up and continued searching. Hence, this Shield of Faith is your well-deserved reward.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"If you ever feel lost in the future, why not take a moment and ponder on the meaning of your journey?\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"The firm belief in our hearts shall guide us through darkness until we reach the light of hope.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Now, I'm sure you're wondering how can you find the Wreath of Hope.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"\"Bring with you your wishes and proceed to the Garden of Promise.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"The Garden of Promise—","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Oh! I think... I might know where it is.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"This is it.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"It is now...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"B-But it used to be filled with irises.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"This is my mom's garden. She used to love flowers and would plant a lot of them when she wasn't busy.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Before she left, she asked me to help look after it, and said she'd come see it with me when she's back.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I watered them every day, hoping they could bloom longer.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"But these flowers only bloom for a short time. They all withered in the end...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Dad told me, \"Don't be sad, sweetie. It's the natural cycle of life.\"","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I understood that. But it always reminds me of my promise to Mom.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I miss her so much...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Now I see, this shield and sword are all treasures that Mom left me.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"And here, I think she probably wanted to make a wreath with me using those flowers...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Thank you, Encore and {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Actually, when I saw Dad looking sad while holding the map, I had the feeling that Mom...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Might have left this treasure map to play a game with me.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Maybe it is like what the grown-ups say, the Gateway of Wishes doesn't exist.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"And I may never get to see her again, talk to her, and tell her how much I've grown...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"But Mom must've wanted to give me a surprise, to make me happy...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I am happy because we managed to find all the treasures she left behind together.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I'll definitely find a nice place to keep this sword and shield safe.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I think we should end our adventure here. Thank you, Encore and {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Tomorrow... You mean right here?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I... Okay then. I'll see you tomorrow!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Encore, {PlayerName}. Sorry for the wait...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Th-Thank you...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I'm so sorry...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Ready. Umm... This stage...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I know...The Wooly Warrior was trying to find the three relics, but I'm not sure if she will find them or not.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"W-will she find it?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Just like us...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"And that... is the moral of the story.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"My feelings...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I know. It's missing an iris. I've always wanted Mom to see a garden full of blooming irises.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"But those irises have already withered...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Find one...?","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I... Of course! But I thought there was no such thing as the Gateway of Wishes. It only exists in the story...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"In the story...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I believe.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Encore, {PlayerName}. Thank you both so much.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I-I finally got to see her, and we talked so much. I told her how much I've missed her, how I found the treasures she left behind, and how I met both of you...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I never thought I'd see her again.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"So, I want you to have this.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Yes! I know you still have more adventures ahead, so I'd like this wreath to keep you company.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I want to go back and tell my dad this story now, and tell him what my mother said to me. So, this is where we say goodbye.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I will! Goodbye!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"You two were incredible...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Encore, {PlayerName}. Thank you both so much.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I-I finally got to see her, and we talked so much. I told her how much I've missed her, how I found the treasures she left behind, and how I met both of you...","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I never thought I'd see her again.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"So, I want you to have this.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"Yes! I know you still have more adventures ahead, so I'd like this wreath to keep you company.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I want to go back and tell my dad this story now, and tell him what my mother said to me. So, this is where we say goodbye.","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036},{"text":"I will! Goodbye!","quest_name":"Small Wooly, Big Adventures","quest_id":121000036}]}